quote><br />\n<br />\n佢無掛住我<br />\n其實好多野都知<br />\n但自己總係好難接受"},{"pid":"17d43408ec9a74add6cde7fb729e9ca06e32b2ba","tid":90301,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔係長文<br />\n係好多段落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過樓主加油啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"4d275db1348bacb226691030f04e7797f04052d2","tid":90301,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:31:40.000Z","msg":"要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8a4d6bb0499698fc676e73839c5f0d60e55c4e","tid":90301,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如何加油<br />\n我應該點做 <br />\n其實好茫然"},{"pid":"7f0de784bd27aa50acaf9ac4da5f5249b0ebdac3","tid":90301,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n時間會沖淡一切<br />\n但直到個刻黎到之前樓主都會痛不欲生<br />\n共勉之.."},{"pid":"09e86c5871fd8a4cbe926d358692f63b12b17612","tid":90301,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"佢唔信人無左邊個會死<br />\n佢話佢心目中自由大於一切<br />\n個心好痛<br />\n穿左個窿咁"},{"pid":"1f66cb34922b5d7e9f535a920e35669b33d6dec1","tid":90301,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好慘<br />\n時間會沖淡一切<br />\n但直到個刻黎到之前樓主都會痛不欲生<br />\n共勉之..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明好sweet<br />\n半個鐘內變左分手<br />\n接受唔到<br />\n仲會ff佢係咪有咩苦衷<br />\n唔想我傷心所以用分手使開我"},{"pid":"df0a71f2951b6e340342c01248458a757e469f92","tid":90301,"uid":4865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"睇完成篇野淨係覺得你好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到「long d」個幾月我已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要分手分到自己咁無尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83cd9757255f6c6e6e0ac67d995c6d16b689a4a","tid":90301,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:39:59.000Z","msg":"撐住呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c2e3518b6362868bf20620c3ba0de3a7ab14db","tid":90301,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完成篇野淨係覺得你好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到「long d」個幾月我已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要分手分到自己咁無尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得自己好無尊嚴<br />\n點解可以咁<br />\n明明同過自己講唔可以咁無尊嚴"},{"pid":"1bbda8c59a94a9cff6bd3edbbcb908cc0106ba91","tid":90301,"uid":43290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:43:30.000Z","msg":"睇完有以下心得<br />\n<br />\n第一 <br />\n愛情入面 你要記住 一定要愛自己<br />\n就好似你隔離fd都同你講要對自己好d<br />\n所以個d咩我就曬你啦你想要自己想做乜就做既係行唔通 你好耐之後望翻就會覺得自己咁做好on9<br />\n(過來人)<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n樓上都講得啱 我覺得女仔係要學識下打扮 <br />\n曾經我ex都好唔鍾意化妝 我都係想佢一時化下淡妝俾我睇 講真個陣由我識佢到一齊個陣我都係見佢素顏 但都會想望下自己女朋友打扮過既一面 所以我覺得可以學下打扮下 少少就好足夠<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n其實我覺得個男仔唔夠愛你 佢係愛你既會更加顧你既感受 所以就咁聽你講我唔係好明點解你話你地夾<br />\n因為我自己覺得因爲鍾意去旅行而覺得好夾有d講唔通🤔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBetween 我想問個男仔係咪射手座？"},{"pid":"97aae579baf2c82448b14c4177656227af9c882a","tid":90301,"uid":56299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得等佢會令你好過啲嘅 咁你就等啦<br />\n不過 你做好心理準備你唔會等到 佢係唔會再返轉頭<br />\n慢慢抽離同學識同自己相處<br />\n做啲你喜歡嘅事 散下心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ada5e98939e8bf8f469683aeb0017260f25e9c","tid":90301,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite